snippet.title: The Silent Arrow 7
snippet.description:
Grinding hard everyday to join @fazeclan, been posting videos for 190 days in a row!!! 
Also, FaZe is the best, subscribe to their channels! #FaZeUp
Sub to Pewdiepie, to Azzy Land, to Kwebbelkop, to Jelly, to Slogoman, to Garrett, to Banks,  to Apex, to Avery, all the FaZe members on here, sub to Jacksepticeye, to Markiplier, to KEEMSTAR, to KSI, to Hamlinz, to Shroud, to Ninja, to FaZeMew, to Agony, ect.. I love y'all!
